  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will analyse factors contributing to cardiac re-operation to determine causative
      effects
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study will collect clinical data on the characteristics of aortic tissue on which
      BioGlue has been applied during a previous cardiovascular surgery. This is a post market
      surveillance study.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
